nodes.title: Download Links
widgets_values:
## Model links (Flux.1 Krea dev)

**Diffusion Model**
- FP8: [flux1-kontext-dev-fp8-e4m3fn.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/6chan/flux1-kontext-dev-fp8/blob/main/flux1-kontext-dev-fp8-e4m3fn.safetensors)
- BF16: [flux1-kontext-dev.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/black-forest-labs/FLUX.1-Kontext-dev/blob/main/flux1-kontext-dev.safetensors)
- GGUF: [flux1-kontext-dev-XX_X.gguf](https://huggingface.co/QuantStack/FLUX.1-Kontext-dev-GGUF/tree/main)

**Text Encoder**
- [clip_l.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/comfyanonymous/flux_text_encoders/blob/main/clip_l.safetensors)
- [t5xxl_fp16.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/comfyanonymous/flux_text_encoders/resolve/main/t5xxl_fp16.safetensors) or [t5xxl_fp8_e4m3fn_scaled.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/comfyanonymous/flux_text_encoders/resolve/main/t5xxl_fp8_e4m3fn_scaled.safetensors)

**LoRA**
- [FLUX.1-Turbo-Alpha](https://huggingface.co/alimama-creative/FLUX.1-Turbo-Alpha/blob/main/diffusion_pytorch_model.safetensors)
- [DreamOmni2](https://huggingface.co/xiabs/DreamOmni2/tree/main)

**VAE**
- [ae.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Lumina_Image_2.0_Repackaged/resolve/main/split_files/vae/ae.safetensors)


**Vantage-DreamOmni2 Custom node**
- [Vantage-DreamOmni2](https://github.com/vantagewithai/Vantage-DreamOmni2)

This node will automatically download DreamOmni2 - Prompt enhancer model based on Qwen2.5-VL.

You can also manually download it from: [https://huggingface.co/vantagewithai/DreamOmni2-nf4/tree/main](https://huggingface.co/vantagewithai/DreamOmni2-nf4/tree/main)

download all the files and copy to dreamomni2 folder.

```
ComfyUI/
 models/
    diffusion_models/
       flux1-kontext-dev-fp8-e4m3fn.safetensors
    unet/
       flux1-kontext-dev-XX_X.gguf
    lora/
       FLUX.1-Turbo-Alpha.safetensors + DreamOmni LoRAs
    text_encoders/
       clip_l.safetensors
       t5xxl_fp16.safetensors # or t5xxl_fp8_e4m3fn_scaled.safetensors
    vae/
       ae.safetensors
    dreamomni2/
        all dreamomni2 files


```
